              "gloss": "(S)he pulls or lifts up"
            }
          ],
          "citation": "Paradigm: Lingua.ge — წევა. https://lingua.ge/verbs/%e1%83%ac%e1%83%94%e1%83%95%e1%83%90/"
        },
        "mo": {
          "note": "მოწევა (vn < მოსწევს, მოიწევს…): (1) moving something heavy hither, bringing in (e.g. harvest); (2) pulling taut; (3) smoking (cigarette etc.) — homonymous noun; (4) moving closer, catching up; (5) (of fruit) ripening.",
          "examples": [
